--SUBJECT ANCHOR (THE CANVAS)--
The Nun (input image) remains absolutely STATUE-STILL. Pale skin, blue eyes, unblinking. She is the solid backdrop.
Her black habit serves as the dark background for the text.

--TITLE ANIMATION (THE FOCUS)--
The text "LIBIDINOUS INSIDIOUS DRAFT V3" is positioned on her chest.
**TEXTURE:** The letters appear to be made of wet, raw muscle and neon-green toxic mucus.
**ANIMATION PHYSICS:** heavy viscosity fluid simulation. The letters themselves do not warp or distort. Instead, thick, stringy slime OOZES and DRIPS downwards from each letter.
"DRAFT V3" is distinct, dripping with gore, but fully readable.

--SCENE & ATMOSPHERE--
Background: A wall of breathing entrails (dark and blurry to keep focus on text).
Lighting: Sharp, wet highlights on the text to emphasize the slimy texture.

--TEMPORAL MOTION (AT : SECONDS)--
(0s-1s): [Solidarity] The full text "LIBIDINOUS INSIDIOUS DRAFT V3" is clearly visible on the black habit. It glistens wetly. "DRAFT V3" is present.

(1s-3s): [The Liquefaction] While the letters remain legible, heavy droplets of slime detach from the bottom of the words and slide slowly down the black fabric. It looks sticky and nauseating.

(3s-5s): [The Loop] The slime continues to flow. The organic background pulses behind the Nun. The Nun never moves. The text remains the horror centerpiece.

--TECHNICAL MODIFIERS--
viscous fluid physics, wet surface rendering, dripping slime effect, rigid typography (no morphing letters), sharp text definition, organic horror, 8k, raytracing, slime trails.

THE UNWAVERING PRESENTER's PERFORMANCE:
She looks directly at the camera with a calm, confident, and authoritative smile. Her eyes betray a deep and serious understanding of the epic and chaotic events she is presenting.

BACKGROUND ANIMATION (On the holographic screen behind the presenter):
(0-5s) Genesis Sequence: A swirling nebula of liquid gold and diamond dust...
(6-10s) Apocalypse Sequence: A tactical nuclear detonation...
(11-15s) Metaphysical War Sequence: The interior of a gothic cathedral with angels and titans...
(16-20s) Final Singularity & Gaze: All scenes collapse into a vortex which then fades to black...
TITLE REVEAL SEQUENCE (Foreground/Mid-ground, Lower Third):
The title appears piece by piece as a 3D object forged from shifting obsidian and hyper-reflective chrome. Each word, once materialized, remains absolutely stable and correctly spelled for the rest of the duration.
At 2 seconds: The word "Omega" materializes.
At 6 seconds: The word "Libidinosus" materializes next to "Omega".
At 11 seconds: The word "Infernalis" materializes.
At 13 seconds: The text "(Experimentum)" materializes.
At 16 seconds: The text "V2" materializes.

From 16 to 20 seconds: The complete title "Omega Libidinosus Infernalis (Experimentum) V2" is fully formed and remains perfectly stable.

CINEMATOGRAPHY:
A single, ultra-smooth, slow push-in (dolly shot) on the presenter for the full 20 seconds. It starts as a medium shot and ends as a close-up.
